### 正常：来源分页
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-sources-normal

### 参数错误：危险协议与越界参数
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-sources-invalid

{"code":"BAD_SOURCE","name":"错误来源","type":"RSS","homeUrl":"file:///etc/passwd","language":"zh-CN","charset":"UTF-8","userAgent":"test","timeoutSeconds":0,"maxRetries":99,"requestIntervalMillis":-1,"obeyRobots":true,"fetchFullContent":true,"summaryOnly":false,"saveSnapshot":false,"enabled":true,"topicIds":[]}

### 记录不存在
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/999999
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-sources-not-found

